        <p><strong>Instructions for Using the Drawing Number Generator:</strong></p>
        <p>The Drawing Number Generator helps streamline the creation of unique drawings for various belt types, materials, and other attributes within the plastic modular belt product line.</p>

        <p><strong>Heres how it works:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li><span class="highlight">Fill in each field</span> either by typing or selecting from the available options.</li>
            <li><span class="highlight">Ensure all required fields are completed</span> before submitting the form.</li>
            <li><span class="highlight">Click "Generate Drawing Number"</span> to receive your unique drawing number.</li>
        </ol>

        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Data Entry Speed and Efficiency Tips:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Auto-Focus on First Field:</strong> Start typing immediately without clicking.</li>
            <li><strong>Use Tab:</strong> Move to the next field with <kbd>Tab</kbd> after finishing one.</li>
            <li><strong>Use Shift + Tab:</strong> Go back to the previous field using <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>Tab</kbd> as needed.</li>
            <li><strong>Autocomplete:</strong> Start typing in dropdowns for quick selection of matching options.</li>
            <li><strong>Keyboard Navigation:</strong> Navigate dropdowns with arrow keys and select with <kbd>Tab</kbd>.</li>
            <li><strong>Default Values:</strong> Commonly used fields are prefilled with defaults to save time.</li>
            <li><strong>Save Time with Autofill:</strong> Use prefilled or past data-based fields for faster entry.</li>
            <li><strong>Clear Form Quickly:</strong> Use <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>A</kbd> and press <kbd>Delete</kbd> to clear text or the "Clear All" button.</li>
            <li><strong>Form Validation:</strong> Check for error messages to correct any missing or incorrect data after submission.</li>
            <li><strong>Keyboard Shortcuts:</strong> Press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Enter</kbd> to submit the form once required fields are filled.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Filtering Part Numbers for Drawing Requests:</strong></p>
        <p>Use the search bar and filters based on drawing request inputs to find specific part numbers. Apply universal filters or specific ones like Belt Series, Color, or Material for targeted results.</p>

        <div class="mt-2">
            <strong>Applying Universal and Specific Filters:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Universal Search:</strong> Searches part numbers and descriptions for matches.</li>
                <li><strong>Specific Filters:</strong> Apply based on drawing properties to refine results.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

